query:
SELECT
                i_item.id AS item_id
            FROM inventory_items AS i_item
                LEFT JOIN (
                    SELECT t_item.item_id as item_id
                    FROM trips_items AS t_item
                    WHERE t_item.trip_id = ?
                ) AS t_item
                ON t_item.item_id = i_item.id
            WHERE t_item.item_id IS NULL
